Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:02.23,Default,EC Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency! Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.23,0:00:03.98,Default,EC Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The band we had scheduled can't perform!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:05.06,Default,EC Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:07.26,Default,EC Girl B,0000,0000,0000,,How will we find a replacement?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.26,0:00:09.18,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I could be of some assistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.18,0:00:10.36,Default,EC Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:13.70,Default,EC Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I forget the name, \Nbut the girl from Class 2—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.23,0:00:15.80,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Gotoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:18.66,Default,Mob 1,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:22.70,Default,Mob 2,0000,0000,0000,,Hold me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:25.54,Default,Mob 3,0000,0000,0000,,You're a living national treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:29.56,Default,Mob 4,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh! Gotoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:33.51,Default,Mob 4,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh! Gotoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:37.11,Default,Classmate C,0000,0000,0000,,...six votes for a haunted house,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:38.86,Default,Classmate C,0000,0000,0000,,and two votes for a candy shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:41.58,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,How long have I been out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:45.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I think I was in homeroom, and they started \Ntalking about festival project ideas...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.84,0:00:46.75,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:49.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Everything after the word \N"unity" came up is a blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.84,DefaultTop,Classmate C,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! So by majority vote,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:53.23,DefaultTop,Classmate C,0000,0000,0000,,Class 2's project will be \Na maid and butler cafe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:55.89,Default,Classmate X,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to get lots of maid uniforms!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.89,0:00:56.98,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:00:58.88,Default,Classmate Y,0000,0000,0000,,Since all the girls'll be wearing them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.88,0:01:00.20,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,All the girls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:02.30,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Does that include... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:03.41,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:05.16,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Too far outside my skill set!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:12.42,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs18\fnArial Black\3c&H33415E&\c&HEFF6F3&\frz16.75\pos(354.5,87)}Grave Cafe\N{\fs10}This way to the afterlife
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.60,0:01:08.70,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if it was a {\i0}grave{\i1} cafe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:12.42,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A-Afterlife for two... \NSouvenirs from the grave available...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:14.75,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Crud, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:16.78,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I almost spaced out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:22.60,Default,Classmate C,0000,0000,0000,,And if anyone wants to perform on the \Nsecond day of the culture festival,
