Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:27.14,Default,Classmate C,0000,0000,0000,,make sure you put one of these forms in \Nthe box in front of the student council room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.14,0:01:29.89,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Perform on-stage as a band...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.89,0:01:33.57,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I never got to do it in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.57,0:01:38.44,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But I daydreamed about it a thousand times, \Nso same thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:40.53,Flashback,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You feelin' the hype, arena?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:43.68,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I play in real venues now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.91,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,My band's not for fun and games!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:47.40,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's serious business!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:49.98,DefaultTop,Classmate A,0000,0000,0000,,If someone from our class played, \Nthey'd be the coolest person ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:50.96,DefaultTop,Classmate B,0000,0000,0000,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:59.37,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,How'd I end up at the student council room?!
