Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.20,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,An unfamiliar ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.93,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:08.19,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:10.56,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm f-fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:13.95,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you collapsed, so I got worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.58,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:18.82,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:19.94,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:21.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:25.36,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell Kita-san, she'll get \Nall excited, eyes sparkling,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.77,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and insist that we do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:29.79,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I m-must avoid that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:32.08,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:35.02,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll head to work after a little more rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:36.41,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:38.38,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But won't you be lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.48,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll b-b-be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.30,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You've got plans with friends today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:45.52,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but I can cancel them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.97,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll b-b-be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.19,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:49.85,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just take it easy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:04:59.48,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'd really like to perform,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:03.49,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,but I've barely done a real concert, \Nso it's still really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.11,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Although...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.29,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:11.63,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,all the performers in a high school \Nculture festival are amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:13.74,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the vibe is like...
