Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:26.71,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I'm so worn out, \NI can't even watch the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:32.56,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But a loner-type shining at the \Nculture festival is a classic trope!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:33.93,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe I can do it too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:36.73,Default,EC Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, Kessoku Band performs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:40.57,Default,EC Girl,0000,0000,0000,,On drums, Nijika Ijichi \Nfrom Shimo-Kitazawa High!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:48.32,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(564,2558)\bord2\fnComic Sans MS\pos(325,35)\c&H020402&\3c&HE9EBE8&}Wah!  Squee!  So pretty!  So cute!  Look at me!  Waaah!  Wahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.81,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:43.83,Default,EC Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And Ryo Yamada, from the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:44.82,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Mini-bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:48.24,Default,EC Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And on lead guitar, from Class 2... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:49.60,Default,EC Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:54.91,Default,EC Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And on guitar and vocals, from Class 5, \Nour school star, Kita-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:58.50,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(439,1)\bord2\fnComic Sans MS\pos(325,35)\c&H020402&\3c&HE9EBE8&}So cute!  Eee!  Squee!  Waaaaah!  Eee!  Eeee! Waaah!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.84,0:05:54.91,DefaultTop,Audience,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kita-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:56.22,Default,Audience,0000,0000,0000,,We love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:56.22,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:58.50,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(439,1)\fs32\bord2\fnComic Sans MS\c&H020402&\3c&HE9EBE8&\pos(324,75)}Kita-chan!                    Kita-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:58.50,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The fervor gap is too intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:03.81,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:08.51,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta know my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:13.83,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:15.54,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, could you do some work?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.41,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,If you're already on the fence, \NI think you should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:22.38,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,These high school years will \Nbe gone before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:23.75,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:27.52,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I'd know, since I \Nbarely cared about high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:29.86,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,I dropped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.19,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I asked the wrong people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.19,DefaultTop,PA,0000,0000,0000,,I could never drag myself \Nout of bed in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:32.95,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.49,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan's talking to Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.54,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That never happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:39.28,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,She's waffling about her culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:40.25,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Culture festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:43.96,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,She's trying to figure out if \NKessoku Band should perform there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.26,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Performing at a culture festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:47.66,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds awesome! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.51,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Um... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:53.02,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun in a different way \Nfrom performing at a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:55.85,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You've done it before, Nijika-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.00,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:58.98,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.41,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I played obscure songs and totally \Nbombed with the audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:04.01,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you sound proud of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.11,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\c&H422DCA&\frz333.3\move(670,203,390,68,30,489)\clip(m 377 0 l 400 25 425 76 426 127 412 163 390 180 379 210 640 220 640 -1)}SMUGFACE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:06.63,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I've never played with Ryo \Nat a culture festival, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.99,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd love to play at this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:10.94,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:13.60,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we only recently formed Kessoku Band.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:16.70,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to play my original songs \Nsomewhere other than here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:20.12,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, it's a great chance \Nto advertise ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:20.91,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.52,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get expelled for playing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:26.84,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H33&\an7\bord0\blur1\p1\fscx167\fscy127\pos(441,22)}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.91,0:07:26.84,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnTimes New Roman\an8\c&H282A31&\pos(523.5,30.5)}Disciplinary Notice\N{\fs16}Class 1-2\N{\fs20}Hitori Gotoh \N\N{\fs12}Reason for Reprimand\N{\fs8}For singing a song with extremely depressing lyrics\Nat a culture festival intended to hype people up,\Nthe aforementioned is officially expelled\Nunder article 50 of the school code.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:25.11,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,something other than seishun rock \Nat a high school culture festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.84,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:31.30,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I get why Bocchi's scared, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:36.99,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,There's a chance—a likelihood, rather—that \Nyou'll be playing in front of a large crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:40.49,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't have to rush to a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.60,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:47.22,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I still have nightmares\Nabout that concert I bombed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:48.86,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,So you were just acting strong earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:53.69,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, just make sure\Nyou don't have any regrets, Bocchi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.36,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,Wise words.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:56.87,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,G-Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.62,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:07:59.45,Default,Nijika/Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:06.71,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Nijika-chan wants to play \Nat the culture festival too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:13.23,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it'd feel pretty darn good...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:21.64,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.44,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.48,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.82,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could do it \Nyesterday, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:33.85,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Nijika-chan told me to make \Nsure I don't have any regrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:38.01,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and if I blow it, I don't think I could \Nmake it through the rest of high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.95,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already nervous \Nabout playing in a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:43.21,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The thought of being \Non stage at a festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.71,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:51.46,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs16\blur3\bord2\fnArial Black\c&H2260DA&\3c&HADE7DC&\pos(59,64)}Skyrocketing to fame!\N{\blur0\c&H54A1ED&\3c&H0F5BAA&\bord1.5}Let's look into {\c&HFFF3F1&\3c&HE80003&}the members of {\3c&HFFF3F1&\c&HE80003&}Kessoku Band!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:51.46,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\bord1.5\fs9\c&HFFEEF2&\3c&H6B0B16&\pos(619.5,68.5)}The unexpected past of super-popular guitarist\N {\3c&H006B60&}Hitori Gotoh, {\3c&H6B0B16&}whose {\c&HA05C00&\3c&HF5D499&}cool personality, {\c&HB81B57&\3c&HFCABE3&}skillful playing,\N {\c&HFFEEF2&\3c&H6B0B16&}and {\c&H5C48BD&\3c&HE0D3F6&}raw lyrics {\c&HFFEEF2&\3c&H6B0B16&}have captured the hearts of fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:51.46,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs10\c&H20241F&\pos(77.5,349.5)\3c&HA8ABA9&\bord1.5}Hitori Gotoh
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:51.46,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord3.5\fs26\fscx90\fnArial Black\c&H11BD03&\3c&H2FB71C&\pos(382.5,246)}Q. Did you know your high school classmate\N{\c&HAB4EEC&\3c&H51A2E5&}Hitori Gotoh {\c&H11BD03&\3c&H2FB71C&}has become a {\3c&HF6F8F9&\c&H35C1CE&\bord3\blur1}famous guitarist?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.71,0:08:51.46,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1.5\fs26\fscx90\fnArial Black\c&H11BD03&\3c&HF6F8F9&\pos(382.5,246)}Q. Did you know your high school classmate\N{\c&HAB4EEC&}Hitori Gotoh {\c&H11BD03&}had become a {\c&H35C1CE&\bord1\3c&H0B3F4B&}famous guitarist?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.13,0:08:51.46,DefaultItalics,AD,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know your high school classmate \NHitori Gotoh had become a famous guitarist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:54.62,DefaultItalics,Classmate A,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Gotoh-san was in a band back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:56.98,DefaultItalics,Classmate B,0000,0000,0000,,I should've gotten her autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:59.10,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just follow that model instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:00.62,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:04.47,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've got a plan in mind, \NI don't feel so bad about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.31,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.73,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:08.58,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.40,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.73,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:14.16,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I got worried and stopped \Nby the nurse's office again yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:15.77,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,but you were already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:19.18,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really? I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:21.43,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and I turned it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:24.48,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,For the culture festival performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.75,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be on stage as Kessoku Band!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.00,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.48,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,The application must've fallen \Nin the trash can by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:33.95,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What a close call, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:37.13,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put on the best \Nculture festival concert ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:45.00,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why she's been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:47.31,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I was so sure she wanted to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:48.02,DefaultTop,PA,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed very excited yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:48.91,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:10:01.95,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.2\b0\fs18\fnComic Sans MS\c&H05161D&\pos(193,260)}I am a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:48.91,DefaultTop,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:51.37,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to label me a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:54.00,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too late to back out, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:57.32,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,They said you can't take it back \Nonce you've applied...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:10:00.14,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll talk to them tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:03.81,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey-ho! Free booze, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:05.16,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no. Piss off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.04,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.84,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Tell yer sister to be nicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:13.17,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,You like havin' me around, right, li'l sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:16.62,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Kindly depart. We're about \Nto open for business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:19.80,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a death glare \Non par with Senpai's lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:21.87,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:24.11,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her? Somethin' on her mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:27.85,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I volunteered us for the culture \Nfestival against her will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:30.66,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,What? You gonna play there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:33.09,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I c-can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:35.73,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There'd be so many more \Npeople than I'm used to,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:41.82,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,a-and I'm s-scared of performing in \Nfront of people who know me at s-school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:43.95,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.37,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,For you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:47.75,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Payin' you back for before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:50.48,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,My band's playin' a gig tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:51.83,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna come see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:53.44,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:54.45,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,'Course you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:56.19,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for all y'all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:57.39,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:10:58.91,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let me pay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.72,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, for the tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.90,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, don't go there. It's a gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:04.40,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:06.00,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let us pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:09.51,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hang on, do you think \NI'm some kind of broke rocker
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:11.95,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,who's gotta hustle money from teenage girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.52,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:16.68,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Senpai, one bottle of shochu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:17.69,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell, dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:21.26,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhoo, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:26.16,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I might not look it, but our band's \Npretty popular on the indies circuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:26.75,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.87,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they have many hardcore fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:32.15,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Which means we make our ticket quotas, easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.88,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,We even make money on merch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.47,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Then why do you only drink the cheap stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:39.68,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,And you use our shower, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:41.27,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Pay rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:43.89,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You never paid me back for your train fare.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:47.03,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a hustle to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:49.62,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's a reason for all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:54.95,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,All my money goes to paying for the \Nequipment I break while playing drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:56.61,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,So it's your own fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:12:00.41,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan, has she borrowed any more \Nmoney from you that she hasn't paid back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:03.05,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... {\i1}she{\i0} hasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.58,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Garbage humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:09.36,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize for your late repayment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.46,Default,Ryo/Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for our lateness!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.07,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:19.92,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Noguchi-sensei... farewell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.02,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,You really need to cut back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:24.66,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,You never used to drink before \Nyou started playing concerts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:26.09,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:29.56,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, that's no biggie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:32.88,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's all go to Shinjuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.82,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:36.56,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think she can really play like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:36.56,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to say "go!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:39.50,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Getting to see SICK HACK for free...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:40.48,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,My soul is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:44.07,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,SICK HACK? Is that the name \Nof Hiroi-san's band?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.29,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:48.47,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I knew she was good \Nfrom our street concert...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:51.11,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't really know \Nwhat she sounds like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:53.25,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of looking forward to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:58.71,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I v-very much enjoyed the concert...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:00.62,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:01.80,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We're not even at the venue yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:06.68,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my home base, Shinjuku FOLT!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.87,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon in, y'all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:11.90,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,The vibe is very different from Starry's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:14.48,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no worries. It's the same kind of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.74,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i0}is{\i1} a little scary,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.74,0:13:18.36,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,but I feel strangely confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:21.23,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Clubs are the same wherever you—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:25.03,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you for the wonderful concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:27.11,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, it hasn't started yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:30.99,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I w-was a fool to think \NI'd grown as a person...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:30.99,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they're nice people \Nif you talk to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:33.33,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-chan! Mornin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:34.70,Default,Gin-chan,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:37.74,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I m-miss my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:39.46,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten to Ijichi-senpai too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:44.11,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,This is the manager, Gin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.42,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:49.64,Default,Gin-chan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gosh, look at all the cute \Nlittle buddies you brought!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:52.81,Default,Gin-chan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ginjiro Yoshida, 37 years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:55.13,Default,Gin-chan,0000,0000,0000,,Punk rock's my genre of choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:57.96,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,The contrast between how he looks and talks \Nkinda shorts out your brain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.11,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:01.77,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-chan's a nice old guy \Nwith the heart of a pure maiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.20,Default,Shima,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hiroi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:04.07,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:06.90,Default,Shima,0000,0000,0000,,For the millionth time, don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:09.93,Default,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,Our rehearsal's already over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:10.87,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.04,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll all work out, I bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.58,Default,Shima,0000,0000,0000,,Are these the members of Kessoku Band?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:14.79,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:16.73,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,And you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.21,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,She's part of SICK HACK.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.66,Default,Shima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shima, the drummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:21.60,Default,Shima,0000,0000,0000,,A pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:23.50,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a pleasure to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:27.08,DefaultTop,Shima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure our Hiroi's caused \Na lot of trouble for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:29.12,DefaultTop,Shima,0000,0000,0000,,If this will in any way make up for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:29.12,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's so polite!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.98,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, th-thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:32.80,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the other band members balance her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:36.80,Default,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Eliza! I lived in England \Nuntil I was eighteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:38.32,Default,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,This is my third year in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:39.69,Default,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:42.22,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You came all the way to \NJapan to be in a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:43.94,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like J-Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:47.57,Default,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,No. Actually, I came to Japan for Comiket!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:50.66,Default,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanna be in an anisong cover band!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:55.37,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Eliza's always saying anisongs are \NJapan's real bleeding-edge sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:55.37,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The three of them are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:58.42,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Balanced?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:58.42,Default,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,I bought this in Asakusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:14:59.11,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:14:59.75,Default,Shima,0000,0000,0000,,Stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:03.84,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.25,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:07.39,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all the people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:09.05,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,There's at least two hundred here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:12.40,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea her band was this popular...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:14.50,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's Ryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:16.66,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,She was with us just minutes ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:18.06,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.31,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,She's sitting over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:21.98,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:27.85,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,the club classic: the "I'm not like you \Noverexcited sheeple" customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:29.61,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Take in the sound. The sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:31.21,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:34.42,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of band is SICK HACK, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:36.33,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,They play psychedelic rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:40.41,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,A genre that spread in the 1960s as a musical \Nexpression of drug-induced hallucinations
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:43.73,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,whose influence led to many progressive \Nrock bands getting their start...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:43.73,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Senpai talk \Nso much about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:48.56,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I c-can't wait to hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:49.19,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:51.96,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kinda interested in psychedelic rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:52.82,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:55.17,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring all my albums tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:57.60,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's best for a beginner \Nto start from the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:01.28,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Better watch what you say, Kita-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:04.60,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of line will get \Nyou mobbed by fanatics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:24.71,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Up late doing spot-the-difference puzzles
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:26.35,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what fun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:33.17,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,A lost child beckons me to a land of dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:29.96,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Their band's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:36.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The drum's spot-on irregular time \Nsignature that keeps you off-balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:38.74,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,This-a-way, that-a-way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:41.52,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The emotional yet overwhelmingly \Nlogical playing of the guitar...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.52,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Which way is the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.97,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,My life's run out of battery
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:46.54,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And the bass forms a wall of sound \Nthat supports it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:47.36,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,But now it's time, let's party
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.23,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But the most amazing thing of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:52.35,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you how much \NI admire your philanthropy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:53.74,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,is her overwhelming charisma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:57.57,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, all of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:00.65,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,For the time they're standing on stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:01.21,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Round and round and round, let's dance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:01.95,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,performers are heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:04.46,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hot and sweaty and close, you swirl around me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.46,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A band really is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:07.01,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I've got toast spread thick with lies
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.01,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,the coolest thing ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:09.34,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to try?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:13.59,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one ghost, and it's me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:16.72,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan! How'd you like my show?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:19.18,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:22.68,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That was so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:24.34,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's got you so down?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:24.34,DefaultTop,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.34,0:17:26.67,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,We stunk the place up after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:27.69,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.81,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You really were incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:32.07,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But I... er...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:35.49,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You were really shining up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:37.45,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I could... ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:42.74,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme fill you in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:46.71,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Up to high school, I was the gloomy misfit \Nsittin' in a corner of the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:49.80,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Could ya tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:52.96,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's true what they say: \Ngloomy people attract.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:58.34,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes I'd imagine what \Nmy future was gonna look like,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:01.06,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,and I'd think, "C'mon, that's lame!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:06.01,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I started playing rock \Nto make my life's course do a 180.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:10.81,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I was scared stiff of buying a bass \Nat the music shop or going into a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:15.53,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,The whole reason I started drinking was \Nto chill myself out before our first concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:19.91,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's scared when they \Ndo something for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:24.29,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,But you played just fine, \Nboth on the street and at Starry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.08,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,And you didn't even need alcohol to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:28.08,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.62,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Have a little faith in yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:32.58,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,And if that's not enough, \Nhave a drink to take the edge off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:34.69,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm really too young.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:38.84,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd like you to come to our \Nculture festival performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.85,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:51.14,Default,Gin-chan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm adding 100,000 to your tab \Nfor wall repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:54.44,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That one's partly Bocchi-chan's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.41,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:58.24,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the concert's got us all hyped up,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:00.24,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,let's plot our culture festival setlist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:03.66,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan said each band \Ngets fifteen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:06.25,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,So that's about three songs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:07.13,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:09.90,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can't I let Ryo-senpai have some of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:10.54,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:14.79,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She needs to learn her lesson \Nfor bumming off of Bocchi-chan for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:16.63,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Ikuyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:21.16,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan! Don't fall for our \Nwicked bandmate's tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:25.93,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,The three Bs to avoid in a boyfriend are \N"bassist, bassist, and bassist," after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:29.17,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never borrow money from anyone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:30.89,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Then I gift you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:38.65,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You're kind, Nijika. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:42.13,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,The legit gratitude is tugging \Non my heartstrings, darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:43.95,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Just help yourself already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:46.00,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I already know our setlist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:50.55,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking it over since \Nthe culture festival came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:52.46,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:55.41,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We'll put a Bocchi guitar solo \Nin the second one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:57.82,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,To make sure you shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:20:00.22,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's your and Ikuyo's \Nculture festival, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:06.73,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't going all-original in the \Nculture festival a bit aggressive?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:09.35,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,So what? Let's be aggressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:10.95,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,And if we bomb, there's four of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:12.27,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We can split the shame four ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:16.81,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo, are you trying to push \Nyour trauma on the rest of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:16.81,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Guitar solo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.76,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:28.87,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gotoh-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.36,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:39.34,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd thrown out the \Nculture festival application!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:41.44,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But I submitted it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:44.13,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so, so sorry that I lied!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:48.39,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you for doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:53.14,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I w-was pretty freaked out at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:55.60,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,but now I'm kind of looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:59.98,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That wouldn't have happened \Nif you hadn't turned in the application.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:03.43,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm really grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:04.99,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:13.41,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san, I'm going to work \Neven harder at practice than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:17.33,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,So let's make our culture \Nfestival concert a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:20.42,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:27.11,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I really wanted Gotoh-san \Nto perform at the culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:30.43,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Because Gotoh-san is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:32.00,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:35.35,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be willing to coach me \Non guitar after work?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:37.84,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Bocchi coaching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:40.41,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san has her own practice to focus on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:43.11,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I want to practice and get better too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:45.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:46.95,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Humor her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:49.49,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,My lessons don't come cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.79,0:21:50.78,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:54.70,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,How come Bocchi-chan's not with you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:57.43,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Well... she's got make-up lessons...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:05.05,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord4\c&H6D5EEE&\3c&HFAF6FD&}31st Annual Shuka Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:05.05,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan's missing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:07.08,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with not \Nletting my sound die down?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:11.39,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with being young?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:20.23,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why doesn't it stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:22.40,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,The rhythm that I can't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:26.08,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,keeps reverberating through my body
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:30.28,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,The melody playing in my earphones
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:35.08,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,is the only thing that lets me be who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:39.29,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,The sky is tinged in red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:45.09,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,But what color is my soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.49,0:22:46.49,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:51.08,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.08,0:22:54.07,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been searching
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.07,0:22:57.29,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,for something precious (hey!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:23:02.91,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,If everything's going to be lost some day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:06.18,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,let's engrave it as deep as we can (now!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.18,0:23:09.59,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,My most pathetic nights \Nand cackling laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.59,0:23:13.77,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,And days when I couldn't say \Nmore than "You know..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.77,0:23:17.93,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,(I'm alive now, yeah Springtime of life)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:19.86,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with not \Nletting my sound die down?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:23.95,Songs_ED3,ED,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with being young?
